             was indicted for <rs id="t18191201-124-off725" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191201-124-off725" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-124-off725" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191201-124-cd726" type="crimeDate">13th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-124-off725 t18191201-124-cd726"></join>, three loaves of bread, value 18 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18191201-124-victim1309" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Greig
                  <interp inst="t18191201-124-victim1309" type="surname" value="Greig"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-124-victim1309" type="given" value="James"></interp>
